In [1021]:
#https://stackoverflow.com/questions/57082102/feature-importance-using-svms-coef-function
def f_importances(coef, names):
    imp = coef
    imp,names = zip(*sorted(zip(imp,names)))
    plt.barh(range(len(names)), imp, align='center', color='cornflowerblue')
    plt.yticks(range(len(names)), names)
    plt.yticks(fontsize=50)
    plt.xticks(fontsize=50)
    plt.xlabel('weight', fontsize=50)
    plt.ylabel('feature', fontsize=50)
In [1023]:
